Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.88,0:00:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He was released?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.00,0:00:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NJohan Liebert was released this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.30,0:00:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard he suddenly fainted,\Nbut I guess it was not serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.94,0:00:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you at the library a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you a librarian\Nat the university library?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right? He was released, was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.95,0:00:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear it.\NI was so worried when it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He faint right in front of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.12,0:00:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He was looking for a book\Nand I was helping him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.38,0:00:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he suddenly fainted?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. But first, he screamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He did?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He was looking at a picture book,\Nand when he turned the page, he screamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.35,0:00:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you take it easy\Na little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your EEG results were normal though,\Nso your brain is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.53,0:02:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in perfect health.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The doctor thinks it was caused\Nby anemia or fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If not, then he said you must have\Nexperienced some kind of incredible shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.83,0:02:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I didn't know\Nyou have a surgery scar on your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate, take a break from work\Nand school and take it easy for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter arrived for you\Nwhile you were in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.18,0:03:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have a return address.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt it is a letter bomb though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.07,0:03:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The Red Hindenburg.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You look awfully wholesome\Nto be wandering around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be lost.\NOr maybe you are here to pop your cherry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.77,0:03:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be gentle with you\Nand teach you the ropes. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard of the Red Hindenburg?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:04:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It says the Red Hindenburg is around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What? At your age?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've already got\Nsome pretty damn weird fetishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.72,0:04:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a fix. Give me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the Red Hindenburg up these stairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a seat right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah yes, there's that face of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Such good looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.08,0:05:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you with Schuwald on the TV news.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So now you're the Red Hindenburg\Nafter pretending to be Margot Langer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And before that, I was Blue Sophie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Names don't mean anything anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Johan Liebert?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:06:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate,\Nit's the name my boyfriend calls me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right behind that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.12,0:06:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't try anything funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got a big gun\Ncocked and ready behind that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The one in his pants is pretty big too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I was impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be\Na hell of a scheme you worked out
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,to cozy up to that fat cat Schuwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That was pretty impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember when you brought\Nthat young guy Fahren to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would've thought\NSchuwald's actual son would show up later?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That poor Fahren guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you were done with him,\Nyou had him kill himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:07:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's taken me a whole two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.09,0:07:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, it was two years ago that\Nthe real Margot Langer opportunely died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When she died,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to reap the benefits\Nof using her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't like I was close to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She wasn't a whore anymore.\NShe had gotten out of the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All I had to do was loosen her up\Nwith a few drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She probably had no one\Nto speak to for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Once she was drunk, a few crocodile tears\Nfrom me and she blabbed everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All about her romance with Schuwald\Nand her son she gave up for adoption.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the woman got herself killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that let me pretend to be Margot Langer\Nand squeeze a bundle out of Schuwald.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.31,0:08:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The police concluded that\Nshe was murdered by a random attacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet they never had a clue she was\Njust a small part of a huge scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's what happened\Nto that poor detective Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If only he hadn't stuck\Nhis nose in things,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,he never would've killed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's the body count now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,All right,\Nthat's enough pleasant reminiscing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to get down to business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't even think about\Ntrying to squirm your way out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, make me an offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you deaf?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think is the ultimate fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd already reached\Nthe depths of the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to change the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I've seen…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,even deeper darkness beyond it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can just walk away?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm through with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.04,0:09:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in Schuwald anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't screw around with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I don't even exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it with your crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey! Get out here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey! What are you doing? Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have one of your balloons?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Use this to get your fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,CARSTENSEN STREET\N(MUNICH)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! When is it our turn?\NHe's bleeding from his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-Screw you! My kid's first!\N-It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-Quit whining! It is just a broken arm!\N-It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut out the racket\Nand wait for your darn turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Crying won't help anyone anyway.\NThere's only one great doctor here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that long stick thing\Nyou are carrying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.82,0:11:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, is the doctor here really that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You better believe it. Without this\Ndoctor, all the Asians around here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,especially the Vietnamese, would be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not Vietnamese, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:11:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You look pretty pale,\Nbut the injured go first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, sit down and wait your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and see my pal, doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My kid's first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-Excuse me.\N-Hey, what's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait your turn, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, doctor. There's something\NI would like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit making me repeat myself!\NWait outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.87,0:12:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have time for you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman and what's more…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear me? Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm suturing now. Don't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything happens to him,\Nit'll be your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a stab wound to the thigh.\NMust be from a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Her suturing is very neat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.48,0:12:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You should insert a drainage tube.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just butt out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, then you need to get him\Nto a proper hospital right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A proper hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-This is a proper--\N-It's no hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just from looking at you,\NI can tell you're not a real doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could take him to a proper hospital,\NI already would have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the people here are\Nundocumented or illegal immigrants.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If they went to a real hospital,\Nthey'd be seized right away
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and sent back to their country.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How many of them
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,do you think have died because\Nthey couldn't go to a proper hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.28,0:13:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't preach about things\Nyou are ignorant of.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Put in a drainage tube.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The knife\Nhe was stabbed with was probably dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't insert a drainage tube,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the wound will get infected\Nand cause an abscess!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Remove one or two stitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:13:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:14:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Insert the drainage tube\Nabout five centimeters in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.03,0:14:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.37,0:14:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:15:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The patients told me you've been working\Nfor 48 hours straight without rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I checked on the other patients\Nyou'd already treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty darn good\Nfor an underground doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Seventeen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding! You're so young,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.46,0:15:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're practically like a real GP.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I just happened to be here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,when the doctor that used to run it\Ndisappeared and left all his equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Having the equipment\Ndoesn't make you a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you learn what you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My father used to be a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"Used to?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a doctor in Vietnam
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and brought me with him\Nwhen he came to study in East Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He stayed on here\Nand opened a small clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But when the wall came down,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,he kept doing what he could to help\Nthe people who would come here from Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:15:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But then…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,some neo-Nazi punk killed my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He was killed just because\Nhis skin was a different color.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was all on my own then\Nand was sent to foster care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then a German family adopted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But they only took me in\Nso they'd look like good Samaritans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Look how we saved\Nthis poor yellow-skinned girl."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.04,0:16:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So I ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I was little,\NI would help my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.09,0:16:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I read a lot of the medical books\Nhe left behind too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I made up my mind\Nto carry on the work my father was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Step aside. I'll finish up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.\NTake it easy until it heals, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.39,0:16:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I took care of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You should go back\Nand study to become a proper doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,People who study hard\Nin this country can find opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see that you are a real doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You just don't want\Namateurs like me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.17,0:17:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean. All I'm saying--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Without me around,\Nwhat'll happen to these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'll take care of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no reason--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My pimp. He lost his temper… and shot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.32,0:17:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she walk all the way here\Neven after being shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.65,0:17:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom said you could fix her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're kidding!\N-Save her! Please, save my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.33,0:18:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. It'll be all right.\NLeave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mom!\N-She is a street walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They're always the ones\Nthis kind of thing happens to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to do something for her,\Nbut this is beyond me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Put her on the operating table.\NGrab her legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.23,0:18:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's useless! This is one time\Nthat we have to go to a real hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be dead before we get her there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the skills for this!\NThere's nothing I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as your patient breathes,\Nnever ever give up hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.63,0:18:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If her celiac artery had been damaged,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.46,0:18:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,her BP would have dropped\Nand she'd have gone into shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But if she was able to walk\Nall the way here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:19:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,she's still in pre-shock\Nand her BP is only falling slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.93,0:19:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging from the gunshot wound,\Nit's likely her spleen has been damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, if we perform emergency\Nsurgery while infusing blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,there is hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.03,0:19:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let us begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the scalpel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems to be sleeping soundly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.56,0:19:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Miraculously,\Nthere was no damage to bones, intestines,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.85,0:19:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,or any other part of her digestive system.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.10,0:19:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She's lucky all we had to do\Nwas remove the damaged part of her spleen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.65,0:19:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That was magnificent surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Only because you were helping me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.30,0:20:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I only came here\Nbecause I had something to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw this newspaper article.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.43,0:20:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Blue Sophie,\Naka the Red Hindenburg.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.94,0:20:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you were first\Non the scene of this prostitute's murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.07,0:20:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you describe the scene to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.87,0:20:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That night, someone from\Nthat area called, so I went.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd been shot through the head.\NShe died instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen murders like that many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:20:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But this one was a first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The feeling I got\Nwhen I entered that room…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a robbery\Nor motivated by malice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.73,0:21:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She was just killed for the heck of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.57,0:21:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.12,0:21:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you're in the darkness,\Nyou just sink deeper into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your light shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you study hard.\NI know you can become a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.55,0:21:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll make a fine doctor for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Where are you going, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,To me, it seems like
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.94,0:21:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you're the one\Nwho's sinking into the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.03,0:22:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll come back, won't you, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.56,0:23:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitle translation by: Brian Athey
